high_descs: Turn around and stand at the end of the green table near the silverware.
Pick the butter knife up from the table.
Put the knife in the bowl.
Pick the silver bowl up from the table.
Go right and stand in front of the sink, facing the stove.
Put the bowl on the counter to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a knife in it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn to the right and walk to the island.
Pick up the knife that is beside the spoon.
Place the knife into the cocktail glass on the island.
Pick up the glass from the island.
Turn right and walk toward the sink and then turn to the right.
Place the glass on the counter beside the sink.
anns.task_desc: Moving a cocktail glass holding a knife fro the island to the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and head to the kitchen island
Grab the small knife that is on the kitchen island
Put the knife back on the kitchen island
Grab the ladle that is on the kitchen island
Turn to your right and walk to the counter
Place the ladle on the counter that's to the right of the sink
anns.task_desc: Placing a ladle onto the counter
